The service was friendly upon our arrival for takeout, and gave us plenty of extra parmesan and peppers. And, everything was hot and fast and ready for pick up.  The not-so-good: Due to the special toppings, the prices are a little bit higher than I would've liked. The breadsticks were also disappointing compared to the pizza and garlic knots.
